          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: requires keyword input and manual publishing configuration — not truly autonomous</h4><p>Koala.sh generates great articles when you give it a keyword. It doesn't find keywords, and the publishing setup requires per-site configuration.</p></div></li>
