        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">SEOWriting.ai generates fully-formatted SEO articles with headings, FAQs, meta descriptions, and schema markup in a single generation step. The bulk article mode lets you queue 20–50 articles from a keyword list and generate them in batch. WordPress auto-posting is available on paid plans. The article quality is consistent but not brand-voiced. Strong for content marketers running high-volume campaigns across multiple sites.</p>
