          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>Best-in-class NLP content scoring — the Content Score agencies use to validate quality</h4><p>Articles scored with Surfer consistently outrank unscored content targeting the same keywords. This is the tool most agencies use internally.</p></div></li>
