      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What is an SEO content autopilot tool?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">An SEO content autopilot tool researches keywords, writes SEO-optimized articles, and publishes them to your site automatically — without manual input at each step. The best tools handle the full pipeline: keyword identification, brief, article generation, on-page optimization, and CMS publishing on a recurring schedule.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Can AI autopilot content actually rank on Google?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Yes. Google ranks helpful, accurate content regardless of how it was written. theStacc's articles have driven an average of +47 new ranked keywords per 90-day period across test sites, with Surfer Content Scores averaging 85+. The key factors are entity coverage, proper structure, and topical relevance — all of which theStacc's pipeline automates.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How many articles per month do I need for SEO results?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
